  <artifactId>nuxeo-platform-ui-web</artifactId>
  <name>Nuxeo Web Framework</name>
  <description>
    Nuxeo Enterprise Platform: Web Framework, based on JBoss SEAM, to build web
    applications on top of Nuxeo EP. It includes JSF components for Nuxeo EP /
    Nuxeo Core, custom JSF converters and resolvers, REST URL support, REST API,
    authentication management (Basic + Form), BLOB download via REST URL, error
    interceptors, batching management, path handling, etc.
  </description>

